#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Delfadors_Memoirs/scenarios/14_Shadows.cfg:164
msgid ""
"This forest looks quiet — too quiet. Proceed carefully, I don’t like this at "
"all."
msgstr ""
"静かな森のようだが――あまりにも静かすぎる。 慎重に進むのだ。こういうのは全く好"
